{"tid":1122223,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"CC 和 事件","createTime":"2019-04-23T23:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T18:08:17.000Z","uid":52477,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f9d0c3c4c6a86d41900333004b1049309de9ef5d","tid":1122223,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T23:16:18.000Z","msg":"發夢見到以下嘅內容<br />\n<br />\nCC Campaign 無大勢力理會，原因係某大事件無論如何都會發生，其波及程度會令CC Campaign嘅努力白費。<br />\n<br />\n某大事件會影響到數以幾十億計的單位。大部份單位將無法再維持恆常運作。對應事件，大勢力早已著手進行挪亞級別計劃。但刻計劃不能容納以幾十億計的單位，因為未有能力做到。<br />\n<br />\n大勢力的行為，已證明 CC Campaign 將會徒勞無功。Therefore no one give a shit to CC Campaign。<br />\n<br />\n最近係某島國首都發生嘅事，算撚數啦！某大勢力首腦亦曾表示 CC Campaign 係流料。"},{"pid":"52bdbb4925c1a6d1ebdf10704cdae166cc479c79","tid":1122223,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T00:01:43.000Z","msg":"有冇人試下decode?"},{"pid":"613fc1ada08f29aaa8b34b583d39c3d8bd79f880","tid":1122223,"uid":119916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T10:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd4ac6c10651fc3120c6ad700df0aba384092a9","tid":1122223,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"613fc1ada08f29aaa8b34b583d39c3d8bd79f880","tid":1122223,"uid":119916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T10:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:30:06.000Z","msg":"唔係故黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a2a0940eb2dd4d03ae52698717994203a88156","tid":1122223,"uid":119916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbd4ac6c10651fc3120c6ad700df0aba384092a9","tid":1122223,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"613fc1ada08f29aaa8b34b583d39c3d8bd79f880","ti